 lustre-client-utils : Depends: libsnmp30 but it is not installable
E: Unable to correct problems, you have held broken packages.

&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We should not depend on libsnmp30 but rather libsnmp-dev&lt;/p&gt;</description>
